We can avoid some deep nesting and the need for a temporary variable to pass the result of the predicate out of the loop by using an stl algorithm:

```diff
--- a/src/init.cpp
+++ b/src/init.cpp
@@ -1686,27 +1686,19 @@ bool AppInitMain(const util::Ref& context, NodeContext& node, interfaces::BlockA
                 break;
             }
 
-            bool needs_ibd{false};
-

